{"tid":1293707,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請進行投訴","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T16:48:04.000Z","uid":167369,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1fa9453ba3efadfc3eaa7a3a487e7a37d224fe0","tid":1293707,"uid":167369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:37:17.000Z","msg":"警察投訴科：<a href=\"https://www2.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FEGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI%2Fereport_details%3Freport%3DCMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR%26fontSize%3D100&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=408e17a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然無用 但好過淨係上網睇到好嬲而又乜都幫唔到手<br />\n設訴內容可以參考下面並加以修改<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw 記得用vpn<br />\n<br />\n「有疑似警員、穿著灰色上衣之人士在其他市民要求其展示委任證時，發表言論：警察執行職務時無需展示委任證，但根據《警察通例》20章，當中指出「便衣人員不論是否當值，在與巿民接觸和行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。在案發現場的便衣人員，須將委任證掛在顯眼的地方，讓人易於辨認其身分。」<br />\n<br />\n本人極度懷疑該人士嚴重違反警隊規例，有損警隊形象（如果該人是警察），如該人非警察，本人則懷疑該人冒警，促請警察嚴正執法，同時亦要投訴在場每一位軍裝警察，包庇罪犯，而16676更以言論辱罵一群提醒他們執法標準的普通市民，本人促請當局徹查並作出合適處分！<br />\n<br />\n以下為當時記者拍攝的影片：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157821403787448?s=100000246138341&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157821403787448%3Fs%3D100000246138341%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=564f13ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157821403787448?s=100000246138341&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n（另一角度，另一報館）<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2292024767549797?s=100000246138341&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2292024767549797%3Fs%3D100000246138341%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo%E3%80%8D&d=P0gT%2F24t7mhr82HgIt0JlfdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=7056ed2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2292024767549797?s=100000246138341&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo」</a><br />\n<br />\n附件<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61v0zVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61v0zVj.png&h=e3cd79b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe1deba2a267a8ace154a539002170ae52b7a4ad","tid":1293707,"uid":167369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:38:53.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得個人資料唔活架"},{"pid":"519083937565d8ee4b7a0016c4f1b976f7264017","tid":1293707,"uid":167369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:39:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e163f1c6dde89ba86419b82c3c0e627b86ceb7","tid":1293707,"uid":167369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c59c12fd20f9a2627847b1e42483a0ba7aa48c","tid":1293707,"uid":30100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:40:00.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"9cbda6f1a6f773acf0b736aa28f75663286898ff","tid":1293707,"uid":167369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019